       }        var serverTime = null;        var serverTimezone = null;        if (time_status == '1') {            serverTime = new Date(begin_time.split('.')[0].replace('T', ' ').replace(/-/g, '/'));        }        var serverTimezoneMinute = parseInt(serverTimezone) * 60;        serverTime.setMinutes(serverTime.getMinutes() - serverTimezoneMinute - serverTime.getTimezoneOffset());        var formatTime = serverTime.format('yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss');        var returnTime = '';        if(formatTime&&formatTime.indexOf('NaN') == -1) {            switch (time_status) {                case '1':                    returnTime = '开始于:' + formatTime;                    break;                case '2':                case '3':                    returnTime = '结束于:' + formatTime;                    break;                default:                    break;            }            return returnTime; content.label06: function GetValue(data) {        var vdata = JSON.parse(data);        if (vdata) {            if ((vdata.status + '') == '0') {                return '即将开始';            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '2') {                if ((vdata.extra.status + '') == '80' || (vdata.extra.status + '') == '16') {                    return '等待批改';                } else {                    return '已结束';                }            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '3') {                return '待审核';            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '1') {                if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '8'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '112') {                    return '继续考试';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '16'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '101'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '80') {                    return '等待批改';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '32') {                    if (vdata.extra.remain_chance > 0) {                        return '重新考试';                    } else {                        return '无考试机会';                    }                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '0') {                    return '已下线';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '4'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '-1') {                    return '开始考试';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '1') {                    return '即将开始';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '64') {                    return '已结束';                } else {                    if (vdata.unit_info.extra.enabled == 'false') {                        return '已下线';                    } else {                        return '进行中';                    }                }            }        }    }

content.label14: function splicingUnits(price,type){        var priceunits='';        var pricenum='';        var len=price.length;        for(var i=0;i<len;i++){            if(!(isNaN(price[i]))||(price[i] == '.')){                pricenum +=price[i];            }else {                priceunits +=price[i];            }        }        if(priceunits){           priceunits =priceunits+' '        }        if(type ==1){            return priceunits;        }else {            return pricenum;        }    }    function GetValue(data) {        var sdata = JSON.parse(data);        if (sdata && sdata.commodity) {            if (sdata.commodity.display_amount) {                return splicingUnits(sdata.commodity.display_amount,2);            }        }    }

content.label14: function splicingUnits(price,type){        var priceunits='';        var pricenum='';        var len=price.length;        for(var i=0;i<len;i++){            if(!(isNaN(price[i]))||(price[i] == '.')){                pricenum +=price[i];            }else {                priceunits +=price[i];            }        }        if(priceunits){           priceunits =priceunits+' '        }        if(type ==1){            return priceunits;        }else {            return pricenum;        }    }    function GetValue(data) {        var sdata = JSON.parse(data);        if (sdata && sdata.commodity) {            if (sdata.commodity.display_amount) {                return splicingUnits(sdata.commodity.display_amount,2);            }        }    }

content.label06: function GetValue(data) {        var vdata = JSON.parse(data);        if (vdata) {            if ((vdata.status + '') == '0') {                return '即将开始';            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '2') {                if ((vdata.extra.status + '') == '80' || (vdata.extra.status + '') == '16') {                    return '等待批改';                } else {                    return '已结束';                }            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '3') {                return '待审核';            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '1') {                if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '8'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '112') {                    return '继续考试';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '16'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '101'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '80') {                    return '等待批改';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '32') {                    if (vdata.extra.remain_chance > 0) {                        return '重新考试';                    } else {                        return '无考试机会';                    }                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '0') {                    return '已下线';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '4'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '-1') {                    return '开始考试';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '1') {                    return '即将开始';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '64') {                    return '已结束';                } else {                    if (vdata.unit_info.extra.enabled == 'false') {                        return '已下线';                    } else {                        return '进行中';                    }                }            }        }    }

content.label06: function GetValue(data) {        var vdata = JSON.parse(data);        if (vdata) {            if ((vdata.status + '') == '0') {                return '即将开始';            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '2') {                if ((vdata.extra.status + '') == '80' || (vdata.extra.status + '') == '16') {                    return '等待批改';                } else {                    return '已结束';                }            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '3') {                return '待审核';            } else if ((vdata.status + '') == '1') {                if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '8'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '112') {                    return '继续考试';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '16'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '101'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '80') {                    return '等待批改';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '32') {                    if (vdata.extra.remain_chance > 0) {                        return '重新考试';                    } else {                        return '无考试机会';                    }                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '0') {                    return '已下线';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '4'                        || (vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '-1') {                    return '开始考试';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '1') {                    return '即将开始';                } else if ((vdata.extra.last_status + '') == '64') {                    return '已结束';                } else {                    if (vdata.unit_info.extra.enabled == 'false') {                        return '已下线';                    } else {                        return '进行中';                    }                }            }        }    }
